Class ConcurrentTransfer<TYPE>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.helpers.ConcurrentTransfer<TYPE>

    public class ConcurrentTransfer<TYPE>
extends Object
implements org.neo4j.function.Consumer<TYPE>, Provider<TYPE>
    Abstracts a meeting point between two threads, where a reference can change hands. It is essentially a latch where a reference to a value can be set while a thread waits on it.
